[[Image:halo-halo1.jpg|left|thumb|200px.|The Halo-halo]]
Halo-Halo is an exotic fruit mix which literally means, "mix-mix." A refreshing tall glass is filled with: shaved ice, milk (or coconut milk), sweet corn, red beans, coconut sport, a dash of crema de ube and leche flan, sweetened plantains, jackfruit, and topped with a scoop of your favorite ice cream.